Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,개는 지미헨~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,보..보리차여도\N괜찮으려나...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,좀 더 세련된\N음료수가 더...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-귀엽다아앙~{\fna두리둥실}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,여러분, 기다리셨죠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,있지~\N기타로 무니언즈 노래 쳐줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 다음에 놀러 올 때까지\N연습해둘게?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,꼭이다!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,다음에는 언제 와~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이것은...!
