Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.48,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna키즈\b0\fs85\bord6\frz106.8\pos(600,740)\c&HC85614&\3c&HF3F3F4&}림
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.48,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna키즈\b0\fs85\bord6\frz106.8\pos(510,675)\c&H9A80F4&\3c&HF3F3F4&}그
