Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.48,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna키즈\b0\fs85\bord6\frz106.8\pos(445,450)\c&H6A88E5&\3c&HF3F3F4&}기
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.48,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna키즈\b0\fs85\bord6\frz106.8\pos(465,335)\c&H1C47C0&\3c&HF3F3F4&}장
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,너희는 여기에\N자유롭게 그려봐!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,네~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,예...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,무난하게\N로고T여도 괜찮지만
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,그대로 굿즈로 만들어서\N물판에서 팔고 싶기도 하니까♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니..니지카쨩\N물판에 탐욕스럽다!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,여러분한테서\N더 좋은 아이디어가 나오면
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,채용할 테니~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨,\N열심히 해보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 예...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}가끔은 모두한테\N멋진 모습도 보여야지!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,그 꼴로\N진지한 표정 짓지는 말자~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?\N진짜 놀러 온 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,정말로, 정말?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,응~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,언니의 망상이 아니고?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,다 됐어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,오, 어떤 건데?\N어떤 건데~?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:11.53,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs40\bord6\fscx90\fscy110\pos(1200,725)\frz270.9\c&H09010B&\3c&HD403E8&}다 함께 붙잡자！ 승리의 꽃을
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:11.53,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs65\bord6\fscx90\fscy110\c&H09010B&\3c&HD403E8&\pos(755,450)\frz279.1}우승
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:11.53,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs70\bord6\c&H09010B&\3c&HD403E8&\frz271.1\pos(865,630)}결속밴드
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:11.53,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,10)\fn@a두리둥실\fs45\bord6\fscx90\c&H09010B&\3c&HD403E8&\pos(835.668,838)\frz286.7}힘내라
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,컨셉트는
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,『우정』, 『노력』,\N『승리』입니다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,체육대회 때나\N보이는 녀석...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,에에~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,귀엽지 않아요?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐만...\N여기 「우승」은 뭐니?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브에\N그런 개념은 없는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,음, 그게~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,그냥 분위기로\N하는 거죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,그냥 해!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.21,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1880,1040)\fad(500,500)\fna두리둥실\fs45\bord5\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H2727CC&}※ 분위기, 김 둘 다 {\c&H000000&}のり{\c&H2727CC&}로 발음이 같다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,그치만~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,이런 걸 입으면 모두의 마음이\N하나가 될 거 같지 않아요?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}안 그래?\N고토 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,바..반이 일치단결!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFA&\bord2\pos(958.6,981.05)}바..반이 일치단결!!?
