Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:58.50,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,10)\fn@a해탈\frz270\fs120\bord5\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&H9F1A0E&\pos(1337,588.333)}춘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:58.50,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,10)\fna해탈\fs120\bord5\blur5\c&H000000&\3c&H9F1A0E&\pos(1240.999,713.666)}심쿵
