Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}청춘 심쿵 영화...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그것은 아싸찐따\N트라우마 영화 장르
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}제1위!\N(일본 아싸찐따 협회 조사)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 시간도 없으니까\N힘 좀 내자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,안 되겠구만\N이거...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.69,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(1255,440)}펴..평범하단 여자가\N훈남 2명한테 고백받는 게\N말이 되나...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.51,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,10)\fna두리둥실\fs50\pos(1255,450)}그보다 그렇게 귀여우면서\N"평범한 나"라고\N하는 건 뭔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,료한테서도 디자인\N아이디어가 잔뜩 왔는데?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,와, 보고 싶어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,보여주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,같이 보자, 봇치쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,응...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐..뭐래, 이건?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,카레...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,응...??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,이번에는\N초밥이네요
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,얘는\N뭘 하고 싶은 거래...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(10,10)\fna두리둥실\fs75\bord10\c&H220BD5&\3c&H2A16DA&}저녁밥\N어떤 게 좋을까?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(10,10)\fna두리둥실\fs75\bord6\c&H220BD5&\3c&HFFFFFF&}저녁밥\N어떤 게 좋을까?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur4\c&HFCFFC1&\3c&HF23523&}스스로 생각해라!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:39.04,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(1280,775)}훗♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,「카레가 좋겠어요」\N송신~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩도\N진지하게 반응해주지 말고!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,오, 봇치쨩 부활~?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,제 디자인도\N좀 봐주셨으면 해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.31,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,10)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\pos(1280,670)\c&H212728&\3c&HE4EAEC&}지퍼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.31,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,10)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\c&H212728&\3c&HE4EAEC&\pos(1330,795)}사슬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:02.31,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,10)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\c&H212728&\3c&HE4EAEC&\pos(595,745)}찢어져\N있다
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어떨까요...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}개..개 구려어어어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,너..너무 화려했을까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}중학생 남자애들 옷에서\N자주 보이는 수수께끼 폰트네...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,이러면 라이브 도중에\N옷에 더 눈이 가버리겠죠?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,응...\N여러 의미로...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.68,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,그 대량의 지퍼랑\N사슬은 어디에 쓰는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 지퍼에는\N피크를 넣고...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,사슬은\N기타 스트랩도 돼구요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,의외로\N실용적이네!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.52,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\pos(1290,450)}히히힣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.52,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\pos(1320,522)}헤헿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 이걸 채용한다고\N생각하면 될까요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 좀 어떨까 싶은데...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,혹시 사복도\N이런 느낌..이니?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옷은 엄마가 사다 주셔서\N안 이래요
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그래?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번도 입은 적은\N없는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,취향이 아니라
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,에엥~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,봐보고 싶당~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,저도 추리닝 차림이 아닌\N고토 씨는 본 적이 없어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,제발, 부탁이야~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐만 입어보자~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-제발, 제발!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,어어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-제발! 제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-제발! 제발! 제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.34,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,980)}-제발! 제발! 제발!\N\h제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:06.80,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,980)}-제발! 제발! 제발!\N\h제발! 제발!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.90,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,980)}-제발! 제발! 제발!\N\h제발! 제발! 제발~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,괘...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮긴 한데요...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-만세~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}-이건...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-귀...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}-귀여워어어어~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,멋져라~{\fna두리둥실\c&H0000FF&}♥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽 봐봐~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,사진은 좀...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩은 귀엽다구!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,평소에 하는 기행 때문에\N깜빡 잊어버릴 뻔 했네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,저..저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 벗어도...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐, 잠깐만!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 그렇지...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,앞머리도 올려보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,분명 그러는 편이\N좋을 거라니깐!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,어...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,일부러\N기르는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 미용실에 못 가겠어서\N기르는 것뿐인데...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N내가 세팅해주지~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,사양하지 마시고~♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn양재백두체b\b0\fad(00,1500)}끄억…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩이\N점점 쪼그라든다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,얼굴을 드러낸 것으로 인한\N급격한 스트레스에
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,몸이 못 따라간 거야!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,800)}아...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩...\N죽어버렸어...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,새로운 기타리스트를\N찾아야겠네요...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,끄윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,선배!\N왜 그러세요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,갑자기 현기증이...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,네...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지, 갑자기 이 방이\N음습해지기 시작하면서...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}산소가\N적어진 거 같은...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,윽...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,폐에 들어갔다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,윽, 난 몰라...\N나도...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,윽, 안 되겠..어...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}힘이 빠져나가...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨의 저주...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}고토 씨의 저주구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,얘들아~\N디저트 안 먹을래?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}키타쨩이 가져와준\N스위츠를~
